{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.124\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">大卫上行之诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">上帝保护他的子民</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>说吧，<span class=\"pn\">以色列</span>：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">“若不是耶和华帮助我们，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>若不是耶和华帮助我们，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">当人起来攻击我们，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>那时，人向我们发怒，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">就把我们活活吞了；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>那时，波涛必漫过我们，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">河水必淹没我们；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>那时，狂傲的水</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">必淹没我们。”</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>耶和华是应当称颂的！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">他没有把我们交给他们，作牙齿的猎物。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v7\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.7\" class=\"v7\">7</sup>我们好像雀鸟，从捕鸟人的罗网里逃脱，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v7\">罗网破裂，我们就逃脱了。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v8\"><sup id=\"Ps.124.8\" class=\"v8\">8</sup>我们得帮助，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v8\">是因造天地之耶和华的名。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}